graph LR
    RHODS[RHODS Operator]

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    RHODS -->|orchestration platform| K8s[Kubernetes/OpenShift 1.25+]

    %% External Dependencies - Conditional
    RHODS -->|service mesh<br/>conditional| ServiceMesh[OpenShift Service Mesh 2.x]
    RHODS -->|authentication<br/>conditional| Authorino[Authorino Operator]
    RHODS -->|serverless<br/>conditional| Serverless[OpenShift Serverless]
    RHODS -->|pipelines<br/>conditional| Pipelines[OpenShift Pipelines]

    %% External Dependencies - Optional
    RHODS -.->|monitoring<br/>optional| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator]
    RHODS -.->|certificates<br/>optional| CertManager[cert-manager]

    %% Internal ODH Components Managed
    RHODS -->|deploys/manages| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    RHODS -->|deploys/manages| Notebooks[Notebook Controller]
    RHODS -->|deploys/manages| DSP[Data Science Pipelines]
    RHODS -->|deploys/manages| KServe[KServe]
    RHODS -->|deploys/manages| ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving]
    RHODS -->|deploys/manages| CodeFlare[CodeFlare Operator]
    RHODS -->|deploys/manages| KubeRay[KubeRay Operator]
    RHODS -->|deploys/manages| TrustyAI[TrustyAI Operator]
    RHODS -->|deploys/manages| Training[Training Operator]
    RHODS -->|deploys/manages| Kueue[Kueue]

    %% External Services
    RHODS -->|fetch manifests<br/>HTTPS/443| GitHub[GitHub]
    RHODS -->|pull images<br/>HTTPS/443| Quay[Quay.io]
    RHODS -->|pull images<br/>HTTPS/443| RedHat[registry.access.redhat.com]

    %% Integration Points
    K8s -->|API server<br/>HTTPS/6443| RHODS
    ServiceMesh -.->|enables| KServe
    Serverless -.->|enables| KServe
    Authorino -.->|enables| KServe
    Pipelines -.->|enables| DSP

    %% Component interactions
    Dashboard -.->|UI for| KServe
    Dashboard -.->|UI for| DSP
    Dashboard -.->|UI for| Notebooks

